<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪终于停了。” 哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们出去玩儿吧！” 奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈想出了个好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去滑雪吧！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我们没有滑雪板。” 艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，” 爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以租。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡特一家在找厚衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“戴上帽子和手套。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“穿上雪地裤和夹克。” 爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“即使摔倒了，也不会弄湿的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡特一家开车去了 “冬山” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>滑雪场里有很多人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸领着全家去了滑雪用品店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要滑雪板、靴子、雪杖和头盔。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位职员给每个人都量了量大小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她把滑雪装备分给了大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在都准备好了，” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以去滑雪了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家花了很长时间准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他们向外面走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去坐滑雪缆车吗？” 哈利问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还是从初学者场地开始？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不清楚。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以前从来没滑过雪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸很吃惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以前也从没滑过雪，” 他对妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为你会滑雪呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米转过身去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她再次走进滑雪用品店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还需要一样东西。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“滑雪课！” 奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>